+TAKEOVERS
+CHIEF OF STAFF AGENT
+Master Architecture Specification
+Version 1.0  •  April 2026
+Owner: Selmen Hassen
+Project: takeovers-cos (standalone Replit project)
+Status: Draft for build kickoff
+
+Contents
+1. Executive Summary
+2. The Problem This Solves
+3. System Overview — The Four Loops
+4. PWA Structure — The Command Center
+5. Communication Channels
+6. Authority Rules
+7. Tech Stack
+8. Security Model
