+7. Background Jobs
+7.1 Dispatch worker
+Triggered when a task transitions from 'captured' to ready-to-dispatch. Runs the full pipeline (resolve → tier → draft → send-or-queue). If Tier A: sends immediately and updates task status to 'dispatched'. If Tier B: creates a draft row, sends a push notification.
+7.2 Outbound SMS queue
+BullMQ queue for outbound SMS to enforce rate limiting and retry logic. Each job: tries Twilio send, on failure with retryable error code → exponential backoff up to 3 retries. On non-retryable error → log error, mark message status, alert via Sentry.
+7.3 Outbound email queue
+Same pattern for Gmail API sends. Handles OAuth token refresh transparently — if access token is expired, use refresh token to get a new one before sending.
