+Once Phase 2 is in production with the dispatch flag enabled, you've solved the dispatch failure mode. The agent now closes the gap between brain-dump and team. Phase 3 adds email handling. Phase 4 adds follow-up — the chase loop that prevents Fareharbor-style fires.
