+9. Background Jobs
+9.1 Incremental sync (every 5 min)
+For each connected email account: call users.history.list since last_history_id, fetch new messages, run classification pipeline.
+9.2 Watch renewal (every 24 hours)
+Gmail's users.watch needs to be renewed every 7 days. Run a daily cron to check expiry on each account and renew if within 48 hours of expiry.
+9.3 Token refresh (on demand)
+OAuth access tokens expire every hour. The Gmail client wrapper transparently refreshes when a 401 is returned, using the stored refresh token. Refresh failures (revoked grant) escalate to Selmen via SMS.
+9.4 Daily inbox digest (optional)
+Once a day, generate a summary of inbox activity: emails received, auto-handled, drafts pending, flags raised. Add to morning brief.
