+9. Background Jobs
+9.1 Project review (daily)
+Runs as part of the morning brief generation. For each active project, computes progress, pace, risk; updates risk_level if needed; generates observations; updates milestones snapshot.
+9.2 Dependency dispatch trigger (event-driven)
+Whenever any task transitions to status='complete', a job fires that re-evaluates downstream task eligibility within the same project. Eligible tasks are dispatched per Phase 2 logic.
+9.3 Project completion check (event-driven)
+Same trigger as above — when a task completes, check if all tasks in the project are now complete. If so, transition project to status='complete'.
