+5. Tech Decisions for This Phase
+Drive client library
+	•	googleapis npm package (same library as Gmail Phase 3)
+	•	Drive picker is a separate JS library — load on demand in PWA settings page
+GitHub client library
+	•	@octokit/rest — official, well-maintained, supports auth and rate limit handling
+	•	Use @octokit/plugin-throttling to handle rate limits gracefully
+Claude usage
+	•	Drive search interpretation: claude-sonnet-4-6 (which file is most relevant)
+	•	File content generation: claude-sonnet-4-6 for routine docs, claude-opus-4-7 for complex documents (multi-section reports, strategic memos)
+	•	Code summarization: claude-sonnet-4-6 — short summaries are fine
+	•	Code grounding for dispatch: claude-sonnet-4-6 — pulling the right snippet for context
+Token budget for code reading
+	•	Files up to ~30K characters get included verbatim in Claude context
+	•	Larger files: include first 5K + last 5K + table-of-contents-style summary of middle
+	•	Multi-file context: tree of file paths + most-relevant 1-2 files in full
